snippet.title: Okabu - Official Trailer (PS3)
snippet.description:
In Okabu, you control Kumulo and Nimbe, members of an ancient race of Cloud Whales, on an epic journey to save the planet from rampant pollution.

Read more about it here: http://www.gamespot.com/615288
